Autogenerated GraphQL Resolvers

----------------------------------

Hi NAME !

I have seen that you follow the graphql-ruby gem.

I am emailing you because I created a gem called graphoid https://github.com/maxiperezc/graphoid

By simple including a concern in your models it will create queries and mutations based on them, using models and relations introspection.

All the resolvers will be auto-generated.
You will be able to query and mutate models and their relations in ActiveRecord or Mongoid.
The queries format is similar to graphcool/prisma.

Hope it helps,
Thank you



